import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import './App.css'
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Switch,
  Route,
  Redirect,
} from 'react-router-dom'
import { v4 as uuidV4 } from 'uuid'
import 'antd/dist/antd.css'; // or 'antd/dist/antd.less'
import SignIn from './Components/SignIn/App'
import Firebase from './firebase'
ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    {/* <App /> */}
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        {console.log(Firebase.auth().onAuthStateChanged((user)=>user))}
      <Route path='/' exact>
     { Firebase.auth().onAuthStateChanged(user=>user)?  <App />:  <SignIn/>}
        {/* <SignIn/> */}
       </Route>
       {/* <Route path='/collab/:id' exact>
          <App />
        </Route> */}
        {/* <Route path='/' exact>
          <Redirect to={`/collab/${uuidV4()}`} />
        </Route> */}

       
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
